HEADWORD: Aggrade
<hw>Ag*grade"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Aggraded</conjf>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Aggrading</conjf>.]</vmorph> <fld>(Phys. Geog.)</fld> <def>To
